thumbnail.description: Cover art for the 2020 Youth Music Festival: Hear the Voice of the Lord
thumbnail.publicAltText: A brightly colored illustration with various colored instruments and technology including a yellow harp, gold trumpet, purple cello, orange guitar,pink piano, blue amp, and purple speaker. They are scattered about a stylized green mountain landscape that has a blue river in the middle with a circular sun above which has the words, "Hear the voice of the Lord". The piano has the words "Uplift and Edify" where the brand name would normally be.
